rc=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf65a31bd02f0609f9b441ae10d85fdbf7fc73f","tid":1396713,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4260a63d01f2612b6882f46a7e160c1336904a9e","tid":1396713,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"希望真係去嘅街坊唔好輕敵，今晚情況係會差過尋晚。記住該走就一定要叫齊人全部走。"},{"pid":"8f4c8f1f42b88c470f432d9fdc4e268ce3d895aa","tid":1396713,"uid":268619,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"休息下好過啦<br />\n個人渣政府都已經話會追究公務員政治不中立<br />\n又去衝馬鞍山  最怕一陣又入公務員數 和理非扭成暴徒/暴徒幫兇"},{"pid":"39c0efb0ec4844bedb8cb7d23f6c8499c060da3b","tid":1396713,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"776a84484b408b99f9d56cf67e45bbadc1d1d8e3","tid":1396713,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b19e6e5fe6e4e16a667911ddf7ef821472a55f3e","tid":1396713,"uid":293677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"再次遊擊??<br />\n經過琴晚一役<br />\nD狗應該會有防範<br />\n風險提升左唔少"},{"pid":"d5132c1c32aa1224e6540af0a45c773633c60a8e","tid":1396713,"uid":35995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTi